General.Name: Omiris AG
General.Description: Philomaxcap AG engages in the investments and financial holding, communications, renewable energy, artificial intelligence, real estate, education, and entertainment businesses in Germany. It is also involved in Internet of Things, agricultural technology, industrial technology, medical technology, smart home construction, e-sports and entertainment, data energy, product distribution, and blockchain technology businesses. The company was formerly known as Phicomm AG and changed its name to Philomaxcap AG in June 2020. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Munich, Germany. Philomaxcap AG is a subsidiary of Philocity Holdings Sdn Bhd.
